-- Money Manager Chais Remains Subject of Criminal Probe Over Bernard Madoff
-- David Glovin
-- 2010-06-15T21:57:03Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-15/money-manager-chais-remains-subject-of-criminal-probe-over-bernard-madoff.html

          
          
             Money manager Stanley Chais and
partnerships he ran remain under criminal investigation stemming
from the massive Ponzi scheme orchestrated by Bernard
Madoff, a U.S. prosecutor said in a court filing today.  
